{"tid":981481,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/MAC沙盒RPG] Hytale集中討論 (1)","createTime":"2019-01-14T10:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T04:01:35.000Z","uid":75610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e438820fc04f0b3c0f360ee5b93ca17ba958a13","tid":981481,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hytale.com/static/images/logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hytale.com%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Flogo.png&h=f2eb57f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.hytale.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hytale.com%2F&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e14c7a75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hytale.com/</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下Announcement trailer先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一個月破30mil views<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o77MzDQT1cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do77MzDQT1cg&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=43f21105\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o77MzDQT1cg</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<strong>FAQ</strong></span><br />\n1. HYTALE係一隻點嘅game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHytale係一隻沙盒RPG，世界觀會有劇情故事support返。同Minecraft個啲一樣係Procedurally generated world，極大嘅地圖會有唔同嘅生態環境同detail位，例如海底, 地牢, 沙漠, 城市etc.亦都好似其他RPG會有boss打等等，起野類似minecraft。詳情可以參考官網, trailer同下面條captainsparklez片。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 有啲咩可以做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話明沙盒梗係做咩都得，鍾意hardcore survival定係casual都可以揀你鐘意嘅playstyle，Settler, 冒險家, 戰士, 鐵匠, 種田流 , 養動物, 商人etc., 隨著世界探索同故事發展你可以搵到好多嘢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。  <br />\n<br />\n3. 同friend玩得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以，<span style=\"color: red;\">隻game support multiplayer</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n4. 幾時出?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時未有確實日期，之後官方有update會keep住係度更新。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 有冇創造模式？<br />\n琴日啱啱宣佈咗有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 支唔支持mods? <br />\n支持，都有tools support玩家自訂minigame，例如玩hunger games，Dota咁打都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CaptainSparklez:</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qjMasVMkhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-qjMasVMkhw&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=04bb3179\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-qjMasVMkhw</a><br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://www.hytale.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hytale.com%2F&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e14c7a75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hytale.com/</a> <br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/hytale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fhytale&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=86084a7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitter.com/hytale</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"http://youtube.com/hytale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fhytale&d=46eS23%2FYCYpUCvpVzq1hNv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ab6ffae2\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/hytale</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hytalegame/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https